  amd64 stable, bug #478252

  28 Sep 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add gnome-power-manager and nautilus-sendto as explained at #480610

  12 Aug 2013; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add missing games and remove aisleriot, it's already under games USE flag.

  01 Aug 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add games-puzzle/gnome-sudoku and reorder games alphabetically

*gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0-r1 (20 Jul 2013)

  20 Jul 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  -gnome-extra-apps-3.8.0.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Make games optional as some people don't need them at all, also allow us to
  use.mask it for arches pending of bug #476710

